<MobilePane @disabled={{disabled}} @activeIndex={{activeIndex}} @triggerVelocity={{triggerVelocity}} @transitionDuration={{transitionDuration}} @lazyRendering={{lazyRendering}} @strictLazyRendering={{strictLazyRendering}} @strictLazyRenderingDeadZone={{strictLazyRenderingDeadZone}} @keepRendered={{keepRendered}} @onDragStart={{action "onDragStart"}} @onDragMove={{action "onDragMove"}} @onDragEnd={{action "onDragEnd"}} @onChange={{action "onChange"}} as |mp|>
  <mp.scroller as |mps|>
    {{#if previousModel}}
      <mps.pane>
        <MobilePaneInfinite::Child @class="mobile-pane__child--previous" @offsetTop={{childOffsetTop}} @scroll={{prevChildScroll}}>
          {{~yield (hash
                     model=previousModel
                     isCurrentModel=false
                   ) ~}}
        </MobilePaneInfinite::Child>
      </mps.pane>
    {{/if}}

    <mps.pane>
      <MobilePaneInfinite::Child @class="mobile-pane__child--current" @scroll={{currentChildScroll}} @setAsDocumentScroll={{true}}>
        {{~yield (hash
                   model=currentModel
                   isCurrentModel=true
                 ) ~}}
      </MobilePaneInfinite::Child>
    </mps.pane>

    {{#if nextModel}}
      <mps.pane>
        <MobilePaneInfinite::Child @class="mobile-pane__child--next" @offsetTop={{childOffsetTop}} @scroll={{nextChildScroll}}>
          {{~yield (hash
                     model=nextModel
                     isCurrentModel=false
                   ) ~}}
        </MobilePaneInfinite::Child>
      </mps.pane>
    {{/if}}
  </mp.scroller>
</MobilePane>